    "body": "With #28792 merged, we can use the embedded ASMap file to benchmark the IP -> ASN lookups. Before, this would have been cumbersome as it required having a real, external ASMap file. We want to benchmark against a real file, as a smaller test file has significantly faster lookups.¥r¥n¥r¥nThe benchmarks cover individual IP address lookups of mapped and unmapped IPv4 and IPv6 addresses along with a multi-IP lookup. For the IPs we assume to be mapped, we assert that they are mapped. Updating the embedded ASMap file might change the benchmark results slightly as some lookups will be a bit faster and others slower.¥r¥n¥r¥n```¥r¥n$ ./build/bin/bench_bitcoin --filter=AsMapGetMappedAS.* -min-time=5000¥r¥n¥r¥n|               ns/op |                op/s |    err% |     total | benchmark¥r¥n|--------------------:|--------------------:|--------:|----------:|:----------¥r¥n|              444.33 |        2,250,565.29 |    0.1% |      5.41 | `AsMapGetMappedASCloudflarev4`¥r¥n|              353.19 |        2,831,377.20 |    1.8% |      5.40 | `AsMapGetMappedASCloudflarev6`¥r¥n|              477.45 |        2,094,475.10 |    0.2% |      5.50 | `AsMapGetMappedASGooglev4`¥r¥n|              362.04 |        2,762,162.94 |    0.0% |      5.34 | `AsMapGetMappedASGooglev6`¥r¥n|           20,065.64 |           49,836.44 |    0.0% |      5.50 | `AsMapGetMappedASMulti`¥r¥n|              347.28 |        2,879,559.63 |    0.1% |      5.33 | `AsMapGetMappedASQuad9v4`¥r¥n|              277.13 |        3,608,402.91 |    0.0% |      5.50 | `AsMapGetMappedASQuad9v6`¥r¥n|                5.26 |      190,197,125.55 |    0.0% |      5.50 | `AsMapGetMappedASUnmappedv4`¥r¥n|               65.93 |       15,167,416.97 |    0.2% |      5.51 | `AsMapGetMappedASUnmappedv6`¥r¥n```¥r¥n¥r¥n_LLM disclosure: while I wrote the initial benchmarks, I had a LLM review it and point out style nits and typos to me._ ",
