        "payload": "tree 4b4e840c21bb06c8868d0ff201cabaf3208cd690¥nparent 7c84a2bdb1625a759d2e8597d5c48415d4d9bfeb¥nauthor 0xb10c <github@b10c.me> 1778519041 +0200¥ncommitter 0xb10c <b10c@b10c.me> 1778692529 +0200¥n¥nbench: add benchmark for GetMappedAS()¥n¥nWith #28792 merged, we can use the embedded ASMap file to benchmark¥nthe IP -> ASN lookups. Before, this would have been cumbersome as it¥nrequired having a real, external ASMap file. We want to benchmark¥nagainst a real file, as a smaller test file has significantly faster¥nlookups.¥n¥nThe benchmarks cover individual IP address lookups of mapped and¥nunmapped IPv4 and IPv6 addresses along with a multi-IP lookup.¥nFor the IPs we assume to be mapped, we assert that they are mapped.¥nUpdating the embedded ASMap file might change the benchmark results¥nslightly as some lookups will be a bit faster and others slower.¥n¥n```¥n$ ./build/bin/bench_bitcoin --filter=AsMapGetMappedAS.* -min-time=5000¥n¥n|               ns/op |                op/s |    err% |     total | benchmark¥n|--------------------:|--------------------:|--------:|----------:|:----------¥n|              444.33 |        2,250,565.29 |    0.1% |      5.41 | `AsMapGetMappedASCloudflarev4`¥n|              353.19 |        2,831,377.20 |    1.8% |      5.40 | `AsMapGetMappedASCloudflarev6`¥n|              477.45 |        2,094,475.10 |    0.2% |      5.50 | `AsMapGetMappedASGooglev4`¥n|              362.04 |        2,762,162.94 |    0.0% |      5.34 | `AsMapGetMappedASGooglev6`¥n|           20,065.64 |           49,836.44 |    0.0% |      5.50 | `AsMapGetMappedASMulti`¥n|              347.28 |        2,879,559.63 |    0.1% |      5.33 | `AsMapGetMappedASQuad9v4`¥n|              277.13 |        3,608,402.91 |    0.0% |      5.50 | `AsMapGetMappedASQuad9v6`¥n|                5.26 |      190,197,125.55 |    0.0% |      5.50 | `AsMapGetMappedASUnmappedv4`¥n|               65.93 |       15,167,416.97 |    0.2% |      5.51 | `AsMapGetMappedASUnmappedv6`¥n```¥n",
